<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>자판기 봇 대시보드</title>
  
  <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
<div class="text-center py-20">
  <h1 class="text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-blue-400">🛒 자판기 봇</h1>
  <p class="text-gray-400 mb-8">디스코드 자판기 봇의 웹 대시보드에 오신 것을 환영합니다.</p>
  <div class="inline-flex gap-4">
    <a href="/dashboard" class="px-6 py-3 bg-blue-600 hover:bg-blue-700 rounded-lg transition">내 대시보드</a>
    <a href="/auth/logout" class="px-6 py-3 bg-gray-700 hover:bg-gray-600 rounded-lg transition">로그아웃</a>
  </div>
  <div class="mt-12 text-left max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">내 정보</h2>
    <div class="bg-gray-800 rounded-lg p-6 space-y-2">
      <div><span class="text-gray-400">디스코드 ID:</span> <%= user.id %></div>
      <div><span class="text-gray-400">잔액:</span> <%= (user.balance||0).toLocaleString() %>원</div>
      <div><span class="text-gray-400">누적 구매:</span> <%= (user.totalSpent||0).toLocaleString() %>원</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>